  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The Moog ladder self-oscillates at the edge — resonance at 0.72, filter cutoff at 900 Hz. LFO2 at 0.03 Hz sweeps through the resonant peak in super-slow motion. Morph at 0.55 sits in the saw-square transition. The DEPTH macro is the performance control: open it and Oscar climbs toward the surface.",
